dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Countywide 1.5m DEM (ft) for Sheboygan County, WI 2004
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived countywide Digital Elevation Model (DEM) forSheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2004. The elevation is in feet, and the coordinate system is WTM (EPSG 3071). A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features. This dataset contains a single file covering the geographic extent of the entire county.
dc_creator_sm: Wisconsin Department of Administration - Geographic Information Office
